text: Demetrios I may refer to: * Demetrios I Kantakouzenos, Despot of the Morea in 1383 * Demetrios I of Constantinople (1914–1991), Ecumenical Patriarch of Constantinople in 1972–1991 ==See also== * Patriarch Dimitrije, Serbian Patriarch in 1920–1930 * Demetrius I (disambiguation), various
title: Demetrios I
